	# This file is part of the "More realistic traffic" mod for SCS ATS.
	#
	# This file contains color examples for various vehicle models and is intended
	# for inclusion in AI vehicle model files. The values given are originally from
	# the paintref web page.
	#
	# The distribution of the colors was based on the information on the edmunds web
	# page. To reflect the color distribution, some colors are listed here more than
	# once.
	#
	# - White colors:  ~25%  (9 colors, 125 times repeated)
	# - Gray colors:   ~21%  (12 colors, 79 times repeated)
	# - Black colors:  ~20%  (6 colors, 150 times repeated)
	# - Silver colors: ~11%  (8 colors, 62 times repeated)
	# - Blue colors:   ~10%  (32 colors, 14 times repeated)
	# - Red colors:    ~8%   (21 colors, 17 times repeated)
	# - Green colors:  ~1.8% (23 colors, 4 times repeated)
	# - Brown colors:  ~1.3% (19 colors, 3 times repeated)
	# - Orange colors: ~0.6% (6 colors, 4 times repeated)
	# - Yellow colors: ~0.2% (7 colors, 1 time repeated)
	# - Gold colors:   ~0.2% (9 colors, 1 time repeated)
	# - Purple colors: ~0.1% (4 colors, 1 time repeated)
	# - Other colors:  ~0.8% (3 colors, 12 times repeated)

